[Personally, I did not care for the tone of this message. I believe it was
meant for Dr. LaBudde but he sent it to ProMED-mail for posting, so I am
posting it. I had to make numerous grammatical and other alterations, and am
hopeful I did not change the meaning too much. I haven't been on a beach
since I saw "Jaws", so I am not too worried about this but it seems to me
that a more direct approach and calmer tone with USEPA might prove more
helpful and enlightening. Perhaps another Moderator would be willing to
continue this string, I won't. -- Mod CHC]
